text: Macrozamia platyrhachis is a species of plant in the family Zamiaceae. It is endemic to Australia. ==References== platyrhachis Category:Least concern flora of Australia Category:Nature Conservation Act endangered biota Category:Least concern biota of Queensland Category:Endangered flora of Australia Category:Flora of Queensland Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
